{
  "stem": "3690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is a small synagogue, and there is some Jews there yet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I inquired and I started walking in the direction they pointed me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Finally I got there about a couple hours later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went into the synagogue, and there was what they call a [NON-ENGLISH] who used to take care of the synagogue, used to keep it clean, sweep it, and keep it in order.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I told him who I am, and I am just escape from a forced labor camp, and my name is so-and-so, and I'm originally from Mukach.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Could you give me any idea or help what I can do?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he says to me, I don't know what to tell you, but maybe one night you can stay here in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the morning, there is a place called [NON-ENGLISH], and there is a Swedish consulate in that street, and they try to give passports and papers to Jewish people under the Swedish protection.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And go there and find out what you can do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure enough, I stayed there overnight and they gave me some tea and a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in heaven.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SOB] And I came to that place where that Swedish consulate was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was kind of dangerous, because was people all around, the watchmen in uniforms, and all that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I says, I just came to fix some plumbing there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had some tools in my hand, in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wasn't cleaned up very well yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I still was looking like with coal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he says, I have to-- they summoned me I should come and fix something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So finally they let me in.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
